"DOS - Main" (20, 21) is also "State" (10,11,12) and "DoS" (13,14,15,16, 18) and "DOS" (17, 19)

BUT DOS also represents  "Agency overall" in at least one of the XMLs, but probably multiple

the XML:s say DoS, but the pdfs say State.
